vrf:
ip vrf VPN-WG
rd 2516:110100000
route-target export 2516:110100000
route-target import 2516:110100000

address-family vpnv4
neighbor 222.7.0.1 activate
neighbor 222.7.0.1 next-hop-self
neighbor 222.7.0.1 send-community both
neighbor 222.7.0.2 activate
neighbor 222.7.0.2 next-hop-self
neighbor 222.7.0.2 send-community both
no auto-summary
exit-address-family

address-family ipv4 vrf VPN-WG
redistribute connected
no auto-summary
no synchronization
exit-address-family
mpls:
mpls ldp logging neighbor-changes
mls flow ip destination
mls flow ipx destination
interfaces:
interface Loopback0
ip address 222.7.0.4 255.255.255.255
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables

interface TenGigabitEthernet3/1
description TO-C1-GSR12016
ip address 222.7.0.146 255.255.255.252
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables
ip pim sparse-mode
no negotiation auto
tag-switching mtu 1508
tag-switching ip
mls qos trust dscp

interface TenGigabitEthernet3/2
description TO-C2-GSR12016
ip address 222.7.0.178 255.255.255.252
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables
ip pim sparse-mode
no negotiation auto
tag-switching mtu 1508
tag-switching ip
mls qos trust dscp
router_ospf:
router ospf 100
router-id 222.7.0.4
log-adjacency-changes
auto-cost reference-bandwidth 100000
redistribute connected metric 0 metric-type 1 subnets
redistribute static metric 1 metric-type 1 subnets
network 222.7.0.4 0.0.0.0 area 0
network 222.7.0.146 0.0.0.0 area 0
network 222.7.0.178 0.0.0.0 area 0
router_bgp:
router bgp 2516
no synchronization
bgp router-id 222.7.0.4
no bgp default ipv4-unicast
bgp log-neighbor-changes
neighbor 222.7.0.1 remote-as 2516
neighbor 222.7.0.1 update-source Loopback0
neighbor 222.7.0.2 remote-as 2516
neighbor 222.7.0.2 update-source Loopback0
no auto-summary
